1
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:39,870
[Better Halves]

2
00:01:40,150 --> 00:01:42,950
[Episode 9]

3
00:01:43,509 --> 00:01:44,430
Hurry up! Let's go see.

4
00:01:44,430 --> 00:01:45,560
Let's go take a look.

5
00:01:45,840 --> 00:01:46,900
What did I tell you?

6
00:01:47,120 --> 00:01:48,780
Xu Ao keeps getting promoted,

7
00:01:48,789 --> 00:01:51,320
Ms. Liu certainly
didn't marry the wrong man.

8
00:02:13,530 --> 00:02:15,230
♪ In this chaotic world, because of you ♪

9
00:02:16,200 --> 00:02:17,500
♪ It's filled with wonder ♪

10
00:02:18,630 --> 00:02:20,780
♪ Only you make me unafraid to give ♪

11
00:02:21,790 --> 00:02:22,520
♪ A vow of life and death to live ♪

12
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:23,750
Ke, you...

13
00:02:23,750 --> 00:02:25,420
♪ I'll promise you verses ♪

14
00:02:26,430 --> 00:02:26,780
I have something to do. I'll go first.

15
00:02:26,780 --> 00:02:29,130
♪ And all I want you in return ♪

16
00:02:30,310 --> 00:02:30,720
Aren't you coming for the food?

17
00:02:30,720 --> 00:02:31,610
♪ Who cares
who the martial legends may be too? ♪

18
00:02:31,610 --> 00:02:32,760
No, I'm not going.

19
00:02:33,710 --> 00:02:34,240
Let's go.

20
00:02:34,260 --> 00:02:35,460
Let's join the crowd.

21
00:02:36,710 --> 00:02:37,840
What is it this time?

22
00:02:42,430 --> 00:02:44,230
Lord Xu is truly a good official.

23
00:02:44,650 --> 00:02:45,310
[Be Kind and Benevolent]

24
00:02:45,310 --> 00:02:48,070
By the mandate of heaven,
the Emperor decrees:

25
00:02:48,240 --> 00:02:50,800
Vice Commander
of the Imperial Cavalry, Xu Ao,

26
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:53,590
brave and resolute, has faithfully
carried out imperial orders.

27
00:02:53,590 --> 00:02:56,570
He's loyal, filial, sincere,

28
00:02:56,710 --> 00:02:58,190
diligent and respectful,
who has pleased me greatly,

29
00:02:58,190 --> 00:02:58,300
and is hereby promoted to
Commander of the Imperial Cavalry Bureau.

30
00:02:58,300 --> 00:03:00,750
[Xu Ao, Vice Commander
of the Imperial Cavalry]

31
00:03:01,470 --> 00:03:01,630
May you uphold the tradition of integrity,

32
00:03:01,630 --> 00:03:03,460
[Liu Yingying, Mrs. Xu]

33
00:03:04,080 --> 00:03:05,610
fulfill your aspirations,

34
00:03:05,680 --> 00:03:07,080
loyally protect the nation,

35
00:03:07,080 --> 00:03:08,840
and safeguard the capital.

36
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,650
By imperial decree.

37
00:03:10,870 --> 00:03:13,200
Thank you for Your Majesty's great favor.

38
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:16,160
Lord Xu, congratulations
on your promotion.

39
00:03:16,430 --> 00:03:18,630
From now on, you'll be
a close minister to the Emperor

40
00:03:18,630 --> 00:03:19,910
and His Majesty's right hand.

41
00:03:19,910 --> 00:03:21,030
Congratulations, Madam.

42
00:03:21,030 --> 00:03:22,960
The imperial edict shall soon arrive,
naming you an honored lady

43
00:03:22,960 --> 00:03:25,020
and bringing great honor to your kin.

44
00:03:34,150 --> 00:03:35,420
Thank you, Sir.

45
00:03:35,710 --> 00:03:37,570
Please accept this small gift.

46
00:03:37,780 --> 00:03:39,990
The Xu family is deeply grateful.

47
00:03:40,770 --> 00:03:41,820
Thank you, Madam.

48
00:03:42,430 --> 00:03:44,079
Lord Xu, you're truly blessed.

49
00:03:44,079 --> 00:03:46,630
Mrs. Xu is known throughout the capital
for her virtue and grace.

50
00:03:46,630 --> 00:03:49,470
Meeting her today,
I see her reputation is well-deserved.

51
00:03:49,470 --> 00:03:50,800
Mr. Li, you flatter her.

52
00:03:51,310 --> 00:03:53,000
Indeed, that's too much praise.

53
00:03:53,000 --> 00:03:54,730
Those words of virtue and grace

54
00:03:54,960 --> 00:03:56,290
are more than I deserve.

55
00:03:57,820 --> 00:03:58,750
This way, Mr. Li.

56
00:04:06,870 --> 00:04:08,130
Darling, please wait.

57
00:04:11,310 --> 00:04:12,840
Madam, what is it?

58
00:04:13,470 --> 00:04:15,800
I've asked the Official Matchmaking Agency
for a divorce.

59
00:04:15,800 --> 00:04:18,190
From now on, we'll part ways

60
00:04:18,560 --> 00:04:19,750
and leave each other alone.

61
00:04:19,750 --> 00:04:20,310
Madam,

62
00:04:20,750 --> 00:04:22,560
why are you doing this?

63
00:04:22,750 --> 00:04:23,760
My mind is made up.

64
00:04:23,870 --> 00:04:25,530
Don't ask any more questions.

65
00:04:27,510 --> 00:04:28,710
I don't agree to this.

66
00:04:29,340 --> 00:04:31,200
Your agreement isn't necessary.

67
00:04:34,060 --> 00:04:36,070
[Official Matchmaking Agency]

68
00:04:36,070 --> 00:04:37,950
Marry Hua Yuerong into the Xu family

69
00:04:37,950 --> 00:04:38,240
[Information Card]

70
00:04:38,240 --> 00:04:39,500
and pair her with Xu Ao.

71
00:04:41,000 --> 00:04:41,909
But...

72
00:04:42,870 --> 00:04:45,090
But Xu Ao already has a legal wife

73
00:04:45,430 --> 00:04:47,760
and he's just been promoted to Commander,

74
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:48,909
I'm afraid...

75
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:51,810
Are you questioning the Lord Marquis?

76
00:04:51,870 --> 00:04:52,800
I wouldn't dare.

77
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:55,630
Hua Yuerong is
the Lord Marquis's sworn sister,

78
00:04:55,630 --> 00:04:58,560
and isn't Liu Yingying
already demanding a divorce?

79
00:05:00,630 --> 00:05:01,960
Forgive my ignorance.

80
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:04,270
The Lord Marquis's plan is brilliant.

81
00:05:04,270 --> 00:05:06,320
Once Xu Ao gets divorced,

82
00:05:06,390 --> 00:05:08,480
it will confirm that
the No.1 matchmaker in the world

83
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:10,140
has made ill-fated pairings.

84
00:05:10,630 --> 00:05:14,160
Then we can marry
Hua Yuerong into the Xu family.

85
00:05:14,630 --> 00:05:17,920
This will perfectly help the Lord Marquis
achieve his grand ambition.

86
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:20,320
Now that you know
go handle it immediately.

87
00:05:22,430 --> 00:05:23,800
Yes, My Lord.

88
00:05:28,920 --> 00:05:30,890
[A Perfect Match]

89
00:05:30,890 --> 00:05:31,950
Let me tell you all,

90
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:34,310
you need to pay more attention
to that matchmaking case.

91
00:05:34,310 --> 00:05:34,990
Yes.

92
00:05:35,390 --> 00:05:36,180
Ke.

93
00:05:38,159 --> 00:05:39,620
Where were you yesterday?

94
00:05:40,070 --> 00:05:42,600
Do you know why we've been
urgently summoned?

95
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:46,270
I've been cultivating myself
at home lately.

96
00:05:46,430 --> 00:05:48,230
I have no idea what's happening.

97
00:05:48,430 --> 00:05:49,560
But

98
00:05:50,000 --> 00:05:51,800
seeing how happy Ms. Deng looks,

99
00:05:52,120 --> 00:05:53,250
it must be good news.

100
00:05:54,610 --> 00:05:56,310
Maybe they want to reward you.

101
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:59,360
After all, you managed to
marry off even Shen Tongyun,

102
00:05:59,360 --> 00:06:00,360
which was one of

103
00:06:00,390 --> 00:06:02,630
the three most difficult matchmaking cases
in the capital.

104
00:06:02,630 --> 00:06:03,070
Exactly.

105
00:06:03,070 --> 00:06:03,430
Yes.

106
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,540
That's possible.

107
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:06,600
If I receive a matchmaking bonus,

108
00:06:06,600 --> 00:06:07,750
I'll treat everyone to dinner.

109
00:06:07,750 --> 00:06:08,320
Great!

110
00:06:08,350 --> 00:06:09,080
Wonderful!

111
00:06:09,100 --> 00:06:10,350
Quiet down,

112
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:11,590
stop guessing.

113
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:14,870
Today there is indeed a major case.

114
00:06:16,870 --> 00:06:19,260
However, this case

115
00:06:19,280 --> 00:06:23,280
can only be handled by the successor
of the No.1 matchmaker in the world.

116
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:28,070
Shi Fa'ke, step forward.

117
00:06:30,910 --> 00:06:33,909
Ms. Deng, I wonder what case
you want to reward me with.

118
00:06:33,950 --> 00:06:34,750
Rest assured,

119
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,070
whatever task you assign me,

120
00:06:36,070 --> 00:06:37,540
I'll definitely handle it well.

121
00:06:37,540 --> 00:06:38,720
[Divorce Agreement]

122
00:06:38,720 --> 00:06:41,050
The divorce case
of Liu Yingying and Xu Ao.

123
00:06:42,430 --> 00:06:43,630
What?

124
00:06:44,070 --> 00:06:45,070
Divorce?

125
00:06:48,510 --> 00:06:50,310
Who did you say wants to divorce?

126
00:06:50,370 --> 00:06:51,570
You heard correctly.

127
00:06:52,430 --> 00:06:55,620
Liu Yingying wants to divorce Xu Ao.

128
00:06:56,830 --> 00:06:58,050
Weren't you always clamoring

129
00:06:58,050 --> 00:07:00,070
to take cases
from the Official Matchmaking Agency?

130
00:07:00,070 --> 00:07:02,240
This is a failed match
arranged by your mother,

131
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:04,500
so please hurry up and fix it.

132
00:07:11,040 --> 00:07:12,470
That's impossible!

133
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:14,000
My mother has arranged
countless marriages.

134
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,730
She's never had a failed match.

135
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:17,700
It doesn't matter if she hasn't,

136
00:07:17,700 --> 00:07:19,160
isn't there one right now?

137
00:07:19,680 --> 00:07:20,960
Look carefully,

138
00:07:21,340 --> 00:07:22,350
this is Liu Yingying's own fingerprint.

139
00:07:22,350 --> 00:07:23,740
[Divorce Agreement]

140
00:07:23,740 --> 00:07:25,550
[Liu Yingying, Xu Ao]

141
00:07:26,190 --> 00:07:27,040
This...

142
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:29,930
Xu Ao just got promoted.

143
00:07:29,960 --> 00:07:32,090
There must be some misunderstanding.

144
00:07:32,990 --> 00:07:36,880
Your mother, the so-called No.1 matchmaker
in the world, made a bad match,

145
00:07:36,880 --> 00:07:38,430
and now our Official Matchmaking Agency

146
00:07:38,430 --> 00:07:40,030
has to clean up her mess.

147
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:42,960
If you're unwilling
to take this divorce case,

148
00:07:42,990 --> 00:07:44,680
then I'll have to
personally go to your mother

149
00:07:44,680 --> 00:07:46,440
and let her deal with it herself.

150
00:07:46,440 --> 00:07:47,840
That won't be necessary,

151
00:07:49,980 --> 00:07:50,520
I'll go.

152
00:07:51,490 --> 00:07:57,240
[Official Matchmaking Agency]

153
00:07:58,860 --> 00:07:59,409
Ke.

154
00:08:00,750 --> 00:08:02,550
What would you like to eat today?

155
00:08:02,630 --> 00:08:04,360
I was just bragging yesterday,

156
00:08:04,960 --> 00:08:07,990
and now Liu Yingying
is getting divorced from Xu Ao today.

157
00:08:07,990 --> 00:08:09,340
I can't talk about this.

158
00:08:09,600 --> 00:08:11,400
Ke, what's wrong?

159
00:08:13,190 --> 00:08:14,110
I'm fine.

160
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:16,080
I have something to do today.

161
00:08:16,450 --> 00:08:17,850
Let's meet another time.

162
00:08:23,350 --> 00:08:24,440
[No.1 Matchmaker in the World]

163
00:08:24,440 --> 00:08:25,580
Ancestors above,

164
00:08:25,710 --> 00:08:28,600
I've encountered
a difficult problem today.

165
00:08:29,100 --> 00:08:30,190
Ms. Deng said

166
00:08:30,350 --> 00:08:32,610
Liu Yingying suddenly wanted a divorce.

167
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:34,500
I dare not tell my mother,

168
00:08:35,370 --> 00:08:36,840
afraid it would upset her.

169
00:08:37,460 --> 00:08:39,190
But I can't ignore this matter.

170
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:42,309
What should I do?

171
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:46,390
Ke.

172
00:08:50,040 --> 00:08:50,870
Mother.

173
00:08:51,150 --> 00:08:52,240
What are you doing?

174
00:08:53,830 --> 00:08:57,800
Are you speaking ill
of me to our ancestors?

175
00:08:58,680 --> 00:08:59,340
Mom.

176
00:08:59,630 --> 00:09:01,510
How could I ever speak ill of you?

177
00:09:01,790 --> 00:09:02,970
I love you the most.

178
00:09:03,410 --> 00:09:05,480
Why are you home so early today?

179
00:09:06,960 --> 00:09:08,750
There wasn't much to do
at the Official Matchmaking Agency today,

180
00:09:08,750 --> 00:09:10,070
so I came home early.

181
00:09:11,110 --> 00:09:11,760
Mom.

182
00:09:12,390 --> 00:09:13,920
I have something to ask you.

183
00:09:15,540 --> 00:09:17,390
Can all couples who are in love

184
00:09:17,590 --> 00:09:18,790
grow old together?

185
00:09:21,540 --> 00:09:22,710
Silly child,

186
00:09:23,030 --> 00:09:25,600
even teeth accidentally bite
the tongue sometimes,

187
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:28,550
how could a marriage be without any bumps?

188
00:09:29,070 --> 00:09:30,960
Then what should be done
when there are bumps?

189
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,090
Must they separate?

190
00:09:33,750 --> 00:09:36,360
Marriage is like a piece of paper,

191
00:09:36,550 --> 00:09:39,170
pure and beautiful, yet fragile.

192
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:42,390
Once folded,
the crease will always remain.

193
00:09:43,200 --> 00:09:44,800
It needs to be carefully kept

194
00:09:44,890 --> 00:09:46,620
and taken good care of.

195
00:09:49,050 --> 00:09:53,390
Have any of the marriages
you arranged had such...

196
00:09:56,120 --> 00:09:58,620
Did something happen to you?

197
00:10:00,120 --> 00:10:00,920
It's nothing,

198
00:10:01,710 --> 00:10:03,940
I just took on a divorce case.

199
00:10:06,550 --> 00:10:09,460
If I were still working
at the Official Matchmaking Agency,

200
00:10:09,460 --> 00:10:11,000
I would thoroughly investigate

201
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:12,720
what exactly went wrong.

202
00:10:12,870 --> 00:10:14,200
If reconciliation is possible,

203
00:10:14,200 --> 00:10:15,790
you should certainly
try your best to mediate.

204
00:10:15,790 --> 00:10:17,550
If reconciliation isn't possible,

205
00:10:17,550 --> 00:10:19,480
when someone's heart has changed,

206
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:21,340
no matter who arranged the match,

207
00:10:21,670 --> 00:10:23,470
don't force them to stay together.

208
00:10:23,470 --> 00:10:25,070
Forcing them to remain bound

209
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:27,380
will only create a resentful couple.

210
00:10:28,240 --> 00:10:32,300
But what if it affects the reputation
of the No.1 matchmaker in the world?

211
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:36,120
Child, come here.

212
00:10:36,490 --> 00:10:38,320
[No.1 Matchmaker in the World]

213
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:41,170
If this plaque has a crack in it,

214
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:45,520
does that mean the name of the No.1
matchmaker
in the world is ruined?

215
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:48,180
If we encounter problems,

216
00:10:48,280 --> 00:10:50,670
we should be the first to step up

217
00:10:51,120 --> 00:10:52,410
and address them.

218
00:10:55,980 --> 00:10:57,920
[No.1 Matchmaker in the World]

219
00:11:00,880 --> 00:11:01,700
I see.

220
00:11:05,590 --> 00:11:07,320
[Xu's Mansion]

221
00:11:13,120 --> 00:11:14,380
Miss Shi, you're here.

222
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:15,910
I apologize for not greeting you properly,

223
00:11:15,910 --> 00:11:16,930
please forgive me.

224
00:11:16,930 --> 00:11:17,930
Hello, Yingying,

225
00:11:18,120 --> 00:11:19,790
I should have visited earlier,

226
00:11:19,790 --> 00:11:21,550
but my family experienced a major crisis,

227
00:11:21,550 --> 00:11:23,120
and I didn't want to burden old friends,

228
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,180
so I couldn't come.

229
00:11:25,240 --> 00:11:25,720
Please.

230
00:11:26,510 --> 00:11:27,520
When you say that,

231
00:11:27,670 --> 00:11:29,200
I feel rather embarrassed.

232
00:11:29,790 --> 00:11:32,150
Xu Ao is a straightforward person.

233
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:35,150
He really has no connections
with the Military Headquarters,

234
00:11:35,150 --> 00:11:36,840
and couldn't help Chief Matchmaker Tao.

235
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:38,100
I hope you understand.

236
00:11:38,320 --> 00:11:40,980
I understand.
Don't blame yourself, Yingying.

237
00:11:41,790 --> 00:11:44,780
Ke, I know why you're here.

238
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:46,740
I'm divorcing him willingly.

239
00:11:47,160 --> 00:11:50,740
Yingying, you've kept this home
in perfect order,

240
00:11:51,140 --> 00:11:52,630
Your efforts really show.

241
00:11:53,490 --> 00:11:56,120
Commander Xu is now rising in his career,

242
00:11:56,280 --> 00:11:57,810
do you really have the heart

243
00:11:58,030 --> 00:11:59,360
to break up this family?

244
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:01,000
My mind is made up.

245
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,210
If you truly care about me,

246
00:12:03,210 --> 00:12:05,010
just proceed with this divorce.

247
00:12:06,630 --> 00:12:07,400
Yingying,

248
00:12:07,630 --> 00:12:09,750
my mother often told me that

249
00:12:10,080 --> 00:12:11,590
even teeth and tongue clash sometimes.

250
00:12:11,590 --> 00:12:12,040
[Noble Feelings and Lofty Ambition]

251
00:12:12,040 --> 00:12:14,240
Marriage is like a sheet of white paper,

252
00:12:14,470 --> 00:12:16,510
pure and beautiful, yet fragile.

253
00:12:16,690 --> 00:12:18,070
If torn too roughly,

254
00:12:18,270 --> 00:12:19,800
it will be damaged forever.

255
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:21,960
For seven years of marriage,

256
00:12:22,620 --> 00:12:25,280
I've poured all my love
into this relationship.

257
00:12:26,480 --> 00:12:27,440
But now...

258
00:12:29,680 --> 00:12:32,110
Forget it, let's say it's my fault,

259
00:12:32,290 --> 00:12:34,350
I just don't want to
live like this anymore.

260
00:12:34,350 --> 00:12:35,070
Yingying.

261
00:12:35,400 --> 00:12:38,490
When Xu Ao came to our house to propose,

262
00:12:38,760 --> 00:12:39,630
I was young,

263
00:12:40,000 --> 00:12:41,970
but I remember my mother asking him

264
00:12:42,330 --> 00:12:43,810
how he, with his ordinary background

265
00:12:43,810 --> 00:12:45,020
and no achievements,

266
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:47,330
could marry the daughter
of the Liu family.

267
00:12:47,330 --> 00:12:48,360
He swore then

268
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:50,580
that if he could marry you,

269
00:12:51,220 --> 00:12:53,090
he would strive to better himself,

270
00:12:53,090 --> 00:12:54,670
to earn the right
to be with you every day,

271
00:12:54,670 --> 00:12:55,730
until you both grew old together,

272
00:12:55,730 --> 00:12:57,260
and never betray your love.

273
00:12:58,080 --> 00:12:58,750
Yingying.

274
00:12:58,780 --> 00:13:00,030
My mother has met countless people.

275
00:13:00,030 --> 00:13:01,640
She wouldn't misjudge someone.

276
00:13:01,640 --> 00:13:02,810
Such deep love

277
00:13:03,450 --> 00:13:05,250
shouldn't vanish in an instant.

278
00:13:05,810 --> 00:13:08,250
Yingying, I can see

279
00:13:08,280 --> 00:13:10,080
you still have feelings for him.

280
00:13:10,200 --> 00:13:12,600
I'm not asking you to compromise yourself.

281
00:13:13,040 --> 00:13:15,410
I can process this divorce,

282
00:13:15,760 --> 00:13:18,920
but I hope you'll tell me the truth.

283
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:21,450
Xu Ao doesn't come home at night

284
00:13:22,930 --> 00:13:24,990
because he stays
at the Flower House.

285
00:13:25,640 --> 00:13:28,560
He has an ambiguous relationship
with Ms. Hua, the manager there,

286
00:13:28,560 --> 00:13:30,960
and she's already pregnant with his child.

287
00:13:32,640 --> 00:13:33,610
Mrs. Xu,

288
00:13:34,500 --> 00:13:35,820
I am Hua Yuerong,

289
00:13:36,030 --> 00:13:38,360
I know you must be curious about me,

290
00:13:38,390 --> 00:13:39,720
so I've come to meet you.

291
00:13:41,680 --> 00:13:42,940
You overthink things.

292
00:13:43,650 --> 00:13:44,580
I'm not curious,

293
00:13:44,730 --> 00:13:45,060
[Noble Feelings and Lofty Ambition]

294
00:13:45,060 --> 00:13:47,130
nor do I want to know who you are.

295
00:13:47,990 --> 00:13:49,250
Madam, you should know

296
00:13:49,600 --> 00:13:52,730
that avoiding something
doesn't mean it didn't happen.

297
00:13:53,580 --> 00:13:55,480
I'm sure you've already heard

298
00:13:55,500 --> 00:13:56,980
that Commander Xu Ao

299
00:13:58,370 --> 00:13:59,650
really likes me.

300
00:14:03,680 --> 00:14:05,630
Tell him to come and speak to me himself,

301
00:14:05,630 --> 00:14:07,030
then I'll grant his wish.

302
00:14:07,670 --> 00:14:11,070
I heard that you've been married
for seven years without a child.

303
00:14:11,070 --> 00:14:13,070
Commander Xu doesn't mind,

304
00:14:13,390 --> 00:14:14,080
but

305
00:14:15,900 --> 00:14:17,200
the child is innocent.

306
00:14:17,690 --> 00:14:18,830
Please, Madam,

307
00:14:18,870 --> 00:14:21,030
spare us, mother and child.

308
00:14:23,860 --> 00:14:25,330
What a despicable couple!

309
00:14:25,640 --> 00:14:27,620
How dare she come here and provoke you?

310
00:14:27,620 --> 00:14:30,360
Everyone congratulates
the promotion of my husband,

311
00:14:30,360 --> 00:14:31,460
but who knows

312
00:14:31,710 --> 00:14:34,040
that my title as the new Commander's Madam

313
00:14:34,480 --> 00:14:36,140
is nothing but an empty title.

314
00:14:36,520 --> 00:14:37,580
If that's the case,

315
00:14:38,160 --> 00:14:39,910
I must confront this scoundrel.

316
00:14:39,910 --> 00:14:41,710
If it's really as you described,

317
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:43,310
I'll make him
stamp his fingerprint for divorce

318
00:14:43,310 --> 00:14:44,610
and set you free.

319
00:14:45,500 --> 00:14:48,450
If a marriage is happy
and the husband loving,

320
00:14:49,900 --> 00:14:51,920
who would want freedom anyway?

321
00:14:54,110 --> 00:14:56,630
[Xu's Mansion]

322
00:15:02,200 --> 00:15:03,200
Here, take a look.

323
00:15:03,850 --> 00:15:04,550
Come on, let's hurry.

324
00:15:04,550 --> 00:15:05,750
Mrs. Li, take it easy.

325
00:15:10,990 --> 00:15:11,630
Lu.

326
00:15:11,630 --> 00:15:12,210
Ke.

327
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:13,240
Haven't seen you lately,

328
00:15:13,240 --> 00:15:14,240
so I came looking for you

329
00:15:14,240 --> 00:15:15,700
and brought you some food.

330
00:15:17,120 --> 00:15:19,400
I know you've encountered some troubles.

331
00:15:19,400 --> 00:15:20,800
Is it about the Xu family?

332
00:15:21,530 --> 00:15:22,790
Why not tell me about it

333
00:15:23,090 --> 00:15:24,820
and see if I can help resolve it?

334
00:15:24,830 --> 00:15:26,440
I suppose you've heard about

335
00:15:26,680 --> 00:15:28,280
the Xu couple divorce matter.

336
00:15:28,280 --> 00:15:29,410
If I don't handle it,

337
00:15:29,550 --> 00:15:32,150
Ms. Deng will surely
mock and harass my mother.

338
00:15:32,420 --> 00:15:33,520
If I do handle it,

339
00:15:33,900 --> 00:15:35,420
she'll definitely use this against me,

340
00:15:35,420 --> 00:15:37,160
drive me out of
the Official Matchmaking Agency,

341
00:15:37,160 --> 00:15:39,020
and ruin my mother's reputation.

342
00:15:39,050 --> 00:15:41,610
Ms. Deng is vicious and cruel,

343
00:15:42,200 --> 00:15:43,430
truly difficult to deal with.

344
00:15:43,430 --> 00:15:45,560
I've always respected her as an elder.

345
00:15:45,600 --> 00:15:47,860
Who knew she would turn on me so suddenly?

346
00:15:48,600 --> 00:15:50,610
If that's the case,
just advise reconciliation.

347
00:15:50,610 --> 00:15:51,740
That's impossible.

348
00:15:52,000 --> 00:15:54,930
Hua Yuerong deliberately
came to provoke Yingying.

349
00:15:55,190 --> 00:15:57,490
It seems those rumors
weren't false after all.

350
00:15:57,490 --> 00:15:59,300
I must deal with these scoundrels myself.

351
00:15:59,300 --> 00:16:00,600
Listening to only one side
leaves you in the dark.

352
00:16:00,600 --> 00:16:02,150
We might as well
hear Xu Ao's side of the story.

353
00:16:02,150 --> 00:16:03,480
I was thinking the same.

354
00:16:04,140 --> 00:16:05,940
But I've waited for several days

355
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:07,410
and he hasn't returned.

356
00:16:07,910 --> 00:16:09,390
Since he's close with Hua Yuerong,

357
00:16:09,390 --> 00:16:11,110
we might as well
wait for him at Flower House.

358
00:16:11,110 --> 00:16:11,910
That's right.

359
00:16:13,010 --> 00:16:14,740
But if we go empty-handed,

360
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:17,080
it would seem like
we're there to confront him.

361
00:16:17,080 --> 00:16:18,410
Why don't we bring a gift

362
00:16:18,520 --> 00:16:19,910
to congratulate him on his promotion?

363
00:16:19,910 --> 00:16:21,270
Then let's go to Xibao Pavilion
to choose something.

364
00:16:21,270 --> 00:16:21,800
Alright.

365
00:16:27,010 --> 00:16:28,270
Look, it's over there.

366
00:16:28,310 --> 00:16:28,910
Is that it?

367
00:16:28,920 --> 00:16:30,980
That's the one you mentioned, right?

368
00:16:31,720 --> 00:16:33,650
Let's go take a look over there too.

369
00:16:36,400 --> 00:16:39,460
Mr. Shi, do you like my handkerchief?

370
00:16:40,550 --> 00:16:44,170
Mr. Shi, you're so strong!

371
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:46,210
You made me twist my ankle.

372
00:16:46,480 --> 00:16:47,540
I didn't touch you,

373
00:16:47,600 --> 00:16:48,240
don't try to frame me.

374
00:16:48,240 --> 00:16:50,270
You suddenly pulled my handkerchief

375
00:16:50,270 --> 00:16:51,030
and stepped aside.

376
00:16:51,030 --> 00:16:51,550
You...

377
00:16:52,300 --> 00:16:54,360
Are you trying to tease me on purpose?

378
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:57,170
My reputation is at stake now.

379
00:16:57,190 --> 00:16:59,170
Now I've twisted my ankle

380
00:16:59,310 --> 00:17:01,110
and suffered your humiliation.

381
00:17:01,320 --> 00:17:02,420
I'm going to your home right now

382
00:17:02,420 --> 00:17:04,750
to have Chief Matchmaker Tao settle this.

383
00:17:05,030 --> 00:17:05,510
Let's go then.

384
00:17:05,510 --> 00:17:07,680
Li Pan'er,
what exactly are you trying to do?

385
00:17:07,680 --> 00:17:09,140
Well, at the moment,

386
00:17:09,250 --> 00:17:10,670
I can't walk properly.

387
00:17:10,950 --> 00:17:13,200
But we have so much work
at Xibao Pavilion.

388
00:17:13,200 --> 00:17:15,740
Mr. Shi, you must take responsibility.

389
00:17:18,160 --> 00:17:20,710
As long as you don't
report this to my mother,

390
00:17:21,170 --> 00:17:22,650
I am at your service.

391
00:17:24,240 --> 00:17:25,349
Actually,

392
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:27,210
I'm not an unreasonable person.

393
00:17:27,400 --> 00:17:28,460
Once my foot heals,

394
00:17:28,590 --> 00:17:31,010
I won't trouble you anymore.

395
00:17:32,680 --> 00:17:33,350
Let's go.

396
00:17:35,470 --> 00:17:36,900
Move along, everyone.

397
00:17:36,930 --> 00:17:39,530
Haven't you seen someone
helping others before?

398
00:17:39,530 --> 00:17:41,330
Mr. Shi looks so tall and strong,

399
00:17:42,180 --> 00:17:43,660
yet he's afraid of women.

400
00:17:48,430 --> 00:17:49,240
I quit.

401
00:17:49,270 --> 00:17:50,480
You beat me again.

402
00:17:50,590 --> 00:17:51,200
Let's start over.

403
00:17:51,200 --> 00:17:52,530
How about we start over?

404
00:17:52,750 --> 00:17:53,950
Let's restart, okay?

405
00:17:55,870 --> 00:17:56,490
Xianxian.

406
00:17:57,640 --> 00:17:58,790
Weren't you supposed to keep an eye on Ke?

407
00:17:58,790 --> 00:17:59,480
Ke hasn't returned,

408
00:17:59,480 --> 00:18:00,540
so why are you back?

409
00:18:03,790 --> 00:18:05,720
Xianxian, why aren't you saying anything?

410
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:06,110
I...

411
00:18:06,960 --> 00:18:08,440
I can't explain it clearly.

412
00:18:08,440 --> 00:18:10,440
It's all because of that young lady.

413
00:18:13,790 --> 00:18:14,320
Son.

414
00:18:15,350 --> 00:18:16,510
Which young lady?

415
00:18:16,880 --> 00:18:18,000
We can have
your mother arrange the marriage.

416
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:19,000
This is good news!

417
00:18:19,030 --> 00:18:20,050
Let Ke go.

418
00:18:20,070 --> 00:18:22,070
Yes, Ke can go.

419
00:18:22,090 --> 00:18:23,350
Which young lady is it?

420
00:18:24,410 --> 00:18:27,410
If Mother hears I tangled with
Li Pan'er on the street,

421
00:18:27,550 --> 00:18:28,810
not only am I finished,

422
00:18:28,810 --> 00:18:31,470
but Li Pan'er's reputation
would be ruined too.

423
00:18:31,610 --> 00:18:33,610
But Ke still needs to be watched over.

424
00:18:33,610 --> 00:18:35,080
What should I do?

425
00:18:35,270 --> 00:18:36,600
My life is so difficult.

426
00:18:36,980 --> 00:18:38,060
So difficult!

427
00:18:40,310 --> 00:18:41,640
Son, what's going on with you?

428
00:18:41,640 --> 00:18:42,750
Which young lady has

429
00:18:42,750 --> 00:18:44,140
cracked that stubborn skull of yours?

430
00:18:44,140 --> 00:18:45,400
Tell me, which family?

431
00:18:45,510 --> 00:18:46,150
I didn't,

432
00:18:46,200 --> 00:18:46,680
I haven't,

433
00:18:46,680 --> 00:18:47,640
don't talk nonsense.

434
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:49,160
What do you mean "nonsense"?

435
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:50,000
How dare you speak like that?

436
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:50,830
Is that how you talk to your father?

437
00:18:50,830 --> 00:18:53,030
Xianxian, explain yourself properly.

438
00:18:54,120 --> 00:18:56,130
Father, brother.

439
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:57,730
I...

440
00:18:58,350 --> 00:18:59,590
I did flirt with her.

441
00:18:59,590 --> 00:19:01,170
What? Flirt?

442
00:19:01,240 --> 00:19:01,870
No.

443
00:19:02,510 --> 00:19:03,310
That's not it.

444
00:19:03,510 --> 00:19:06,350
It's Ms. Li who said I flirted with her.

445
00:19:10,240 --> 00:19:11,510
It's nothing, nothing.

446
00:19:11,510 --> 00:19:13,920
Ms. Li must have been instructed by Lu Chi

447
00:19:13,940 --> 00:19:15,060
to say such things.

448
00:19:16,270 --> 00:19:20,870
Isn't she actually coveting
my strong and mighty presence?

449
00:19:23,640 --> 00:19:24,350
Son.

450
00:19:25,480 --> 00:19:27,110
Do you have some misunderstanding

451
00:19:27,110 --> 00:19:28,510
about what "strong and mighty" means?

452
00:19:28,510 --> 00:19:30,550
Or perhaps Ms. Li's eyesight

453
00:19:30,680 --> 00:19:31,540
is the problem?

454
00:19:32,070 --> 00:19:33,100
What do you mean?

455
00:19:33,310 --> 00:19:34,330
I mean,

456
00:19:34,400 --> 00:19:36,860
how could she
possibly be interested in you?

457
00:19:39,890 --> 00:19:41,090
That does make sense.

458
00:19:55,680 --> 00:19:57,340
This color looks a bit better.

459
00:19:57,720 --> 00:20:00,360
None of these seem quite right.

460
00:20:01,650 --> 00:20:02,520
Pan'er,

461
00:20:03,190 --> 00:20:05,390
what do you think I should give as a gift?

462
00:20:05,830 --> 00:20:07,660
Miss Shi, don't worry,

463
00:20:07,880 --> 00:20:08,860
our Chief

464
00:20:08,960 --> 00:20:10,760
probably has it all planned out.

465
00:20:11,870 --> 00:20:12,740
Pan'er.

466
00:20:12,830 --> 00:20:15,100
What happy news have you heard

467
00:20:15,200 --> 00:20:17,030
that makes you smile so brightly?

468
00:20:17,030 --> 00:20:18,610
Was I smiling?

469
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:23,690
Maybe the honest guy
is just too interesting.

470
00:20:24,400 --> 00:20:25,300
Honest guy?

471
00:20:26,040 --> 00:20:27,500
Who are you talking about?

472
00:20:31,240 --> 00:20:32,240
[Heaven Rewards the Diligent]

473
00:20:32,240 --> 00:20:33,140
Mr. He.

474
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:35,210
Thank you.

475
00:20:35,240 --> 00:20:36,030
Kexian.

476
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:37,630
Ke?

477
00:20:38,010 --> 00:20:39,340
What are you doing here?

478
00:20:40,900 --> 00:20:42,680
Ms. Li, I apologize for the intrusion.

479
00:20:42,680 --> 00:20:43,370
It's fine.

480
00:20:43,390 --> 00:20:44,610
Here are the desserts you ordered.

481
00:20:44,610 --> 00:20:45,950
I'll leave you two to chat.

482
00:20:45,950 --> 00:20:47,310
This way, please.

483
00:20:49,380 --> 00:20:51,220
Kexian, you're just in time.

484
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:53,120
I'm going to meet Commander Xu Ao.

485
00:20:53,430 --> 00:20:56,200
What do you think
I should bring as a gift?

486
00:20:56,440 --> 00:20:57,720
Why don't you come back with me,

487
00:20:57,720 --> 00:21:00,030
and we can pick out
some exquisite desserts.

488
00:21:00,030 --> 00:21:02,240
Ketian isn't still angry with me, is she?

489
00:21:02,240 --> 00:21:03,470
If I come back with you,

490
00:21:03,470 --> 00:21:05,270
she won't throw me out, will she?

491
00:21:05,530 --> 00:21:06,930
She's not angry anymore.

492
00:21:07,160 --> 00:21:09,360
She's been talking about you every day.

493
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:12,040
But bringing food,

494
00:21:12,400 --> 00:21:13,800
isn't that too ordinary?

495
00:21:15,000 --> 00:21:17,150
How about this gift?

496
00:21:19,290 --> 00:21:21,520
Lu, what kind of scroll is this?

497
00:21:21,790 --> 00:21:23,160
No matter what kind of scroll it is,

498
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:24,690
Xu Ao is a military officer,

499
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:27,450
how could he be given
paintings and calligraphy?

500
00:21:35,380 --> 00:21:38,640
This brushwork looks
very similar to Mr. Lin Yuan's style.

501
00:21:40,580 --> 00:21:42,740
It just doesn't have a signature or seal.

502
00:21:42,740 --> 00:21:43,700
But this piece

503
00:21:43,900 --> 00:21:45,590
shows stronger
and more masterful brushwork

504
00:21:45,590 --> 00:21:46,920
than his previous ones.

505
00:21:49,860 --> 00:21:51,630
It might just be an imitation.

506
00:21:52,240 --> 00:21:53,600
How can you give someone

507
00:21:53,620 --> 00:21:55,240
a painting without a signature?

508
00:21:55,240 --> 00:21:57,300
Kexian, you're mistaken about this.

509
00:21:57,640 --> 00:21:59,410
Mr. Lin Yuan's works are worth a fortune.

510
00:21:59,410 --> 00:22:01,210
And Xu Ao has just been promoted.

511
00:22:01,220 --> 00:22:02,710
If I were to give him an authentic piece,

512
00:22:02,710 --> 00:22:04,170
it might look like a bribe.

513
00:22:04,570 --> 00:22:06,900
This imitation has good artistic concept

514
00:22:06,940 --> 00:22:08,330
and excellent technique.

515
00:22:08,330 --> 00:22:10,530
As a gift exchanged between friends,

516
00:22:10,580 --> 00:22:11,480
it's tasteful

517
00:22:11,680 --> 00:22:13,280
and doesn't violate any laws.

518
00:22:13,280 --> 00:22:14,540
That's exactly right.

519
00:22:16,320 --> 00:22:17,190
Kexian,

520
00:22:17,290 --> 00:22:19,190
we need to attend
to some important matters.

521
00:22:19,190 --> 00:22:21,450
We'll visit you and Ketian another time.

522
00:22:27,440 --> 00:22:28,240
You can go now.

523
00:22:28,480 --> 00:22:29,740
Take care of yourself.

524
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:36,880
Lu.

525
00:22:37,190 --> 00:22:37,940
Do you think

526
00:22:37,960 --> 00:22:40,690
Xu Ao is really like
what Liu Yingying described?

527
00:22:40,730 --> 00:22:42,300
I dare not make assumptions,

528
00:22:42,300 --> 00:22:44,190
but seeing is believing.

529
00:22:44,350 --> 00:22:46,340
Let's go to Flower House
to meet Xu Ao first,

530
00:22:46,340 --> 00:22:47,870
then we can make a decision.

531
00:22:50,610 --> 00:22:52,530
[Flower House]

532
00:22:53,140 --> 00:22:54,970
How is the divorce proceeding?

533
00:22:55,550 --> 00:22:56,560
Rest assured, My Lord.

534
00:22:56,560 --> 00:22:59,220
I've sent Tao's daughter
Shi Fa'ke to handle it.

535
00:22:59,270 --> 00:23:00,400
It will be done soon.

536
00:23:00,590 --> 00:23:02,320
You sent Shi Fa'ke to handle it?

537
00:23:02,350 --> 00:23:04,480
You're letting personal grudges
interfere with important matters.

538
00:23:04,480 --> 00:23:05,180
I...

539
00:23:06,380 --> 00:23:08,520
All Ms. Deng wants is to tarnish

540
00:23:08,550 --> 00:23:11,010
the name
of the No.1 matchmaker in the world.

541
00:23:11,720 --> 00:23:12,970
She wants to succeed

542
00:23:13,310 --> 00:23:15,110
while taking all the advantage.

543
00:23:16,430 --> 00:23:17,620
Little does she know

544
00:23:17,740 --> 00:23:20,450
that times and circumstances change.

545
00:23:22,540 --> 00:23:25,650
I finally managed to force
Liu Yingying to initiate a divorce.

546
00:23:25,650 --> 00:23:26,880
Ms. Deng, you've delayed

547
00:23:26,880 --> 00:23:29,620
my sworn brother's important matter
due to your selfish interests.

548
00:23:29,620 --> 00:23:31,670
If my sworn brother blames us for this,

549
00:23:31,670 --> 00:23:33,800
neither of us can bear the consequences.

550
00:23:33,800 --> 00:23:35,700
I wouldn't dare.

