00:37:36,330 --> 00:37:37,630
I had to lie to Mrs. Xu,

829
00:37:38,530 --> 00:37:39,930
claiming I was pregnant.

830
00:37:40,880 --> 00:37:41,580
What?

831
00:37:48,230 --> 00:37:48,840
This...

832
00:37:49,790 --> 00:37:52,390
No wonder Yingying
suddenly wanted a divorce.

833
00:37:54,400 --> 00:37:57,450
I thought she despised me
for being uncouth

834
00:37:57,550 --> 00:37:59,280
and not taking good care of her.

835
00:38:01,190 --> 00:38:01,970
Xu Ao.

836
00:38:04,670 --> 00:38:05,390
Dear.

837
00:38:08,880 --> 00:38:09,540
Darling.

838
00:38:10,180 --> 00:38:11,640
I have never despised you.

839
00:38:11,920 --> 00:38:13,200
It's just that since our marriage,

840
00:38:13,200 --> 00:38:15,660
I haven't been able
to bear you any children,

841
00:38:15,880 --> 00:38:17,880
so I feel I've let you down terribly.

842
00:38:18,150 --> 00:38:21,130
Besides, you've been distracted all year.

843
00:38:21,160 --> 00:38:22,890
You haven't been talking to me.

844
00:38:23,460 --> 00:38:25,390
I thought you had grown tired of me.

845
00:38:25,440 --> 00:38:26,820
How could that be possible, Dear?

846
00:38:26,820 --> 00:38:28,350
How could I ever tire of you?

847
00:38:28,510 --> 00:38:30,510
I can't get enough of looking at you.

848
00:38:30,550 --> 00:38:33,350
It's just that I have
important matters on my mind.

849
00:38:34,190 --> 00:38:35,920
I often neglect your feelings.

850
00:38:36,000 --> 00:38:37,530
Children come to us by fate,

851
00:38:37,880 --> 00:38:39,580
and if they don't, it's heaven's will.

852
00:38:39,580 --> 00:38:41,380
As long as I can grow old with you,

853
00:38:42,400 --> 00:38:43,770
I dare not ask for more.

854
00:38:44,350 --> 00:38:47,100
But you're the sole male heir
of three generations.

855
00:38:47,100 --> 00:38:49,000
Your parents, before they passed away,
instructed me

856
00:38:49,000 --> 00:38:50,600
to continue the family line.

857
00:38:50,820 --> 00:38:52,260
How dare I not listen?

858
00:38:53,070 --> 00:38:54,560
My silly wife.

859
00:38:54,800 --> 00:38:56,230
If we truly cannot have one of our own,

860
00:38:56,230 --> 00:38:57,840
and you still insist on having a child,

861
00:38:57,840 --> 00:38:59,400
we could always adopt one.

862
00:38:59,950 --> 00:39:01,210
Lord Xu speaks wisely.

863
00:39:01,690 --> 00:39:04,220
A marriage is built by two people,

864
00:39:04,520 --> 00:39:06,480
how can it depend on children?

865
00:39:07,040 --> 00:39:09,500
If Lord Xu were to
divorce you over children,

866
00:39:09,530 --> 00:39:11,590
then he wouldn't be a good husband anyway.

867
00:39:11,590 --> 00:39:13,630
Miss Shi speaks the truth.

868
00:39:14,860 --> 00:39:16,320
Do you truly feel this way?

869
00:39:17,950 --> 00:39:21,240
I married you because I love you.

870
00:39:21,920 --> 00:39:23,580
I would never divorce you over

871
00:39:23,710 --> 00:39:26,770
this so-called inability
to continue the family line.

872
00:39:28,840 --> 00:39:30,300
To have a husband like you,

873
00:39:30,570 --> 00:39:32,170
I could ask for nothing more.

874
00:39:34,880 --> 00:39:35,530
Madam.

875
00:39:37,960 --> 00:39:38,620
Lord Xu.

876
00:39:39,130 --> 00:39:40,590
I must have a word with you.

877
00:39:40,830 --> 00:39:43,230
You sent rouge
but didn't tell Yingying about it.

878
00:39:43,230 --> 00:39:44,440
If I hadn't overheard,

879
00:39:44,440 --> 00:39:46,300
when would Yingying have seen it?

880
00:39:46,590 --> 00:39:47,920
It's entirely my fault.

881
00:39:48,760 --> 00:39:50,000
It's entirely my fault.

882
00:39:50,000 --> 00:39:50,920
It's my fault.

883
00:39:51,440 --> 00:39:53,300
I shouldn't have distrusted you.

884
00:39:53,850 --> 00:39:55,310
Neither of you is at fault.

885
00:39:55,360 --> 00:39:55,950
Blame me

886
00:39:56,270 --> 00:39:58,070
for not eavesdropping earlier.

887
00:39:58,390 --> 00:40:01,070
Ke, what exactly is going on?

888
00:40:13,080 --> 00:40:15,370
Didn't we agree not to meet these days?

889
00:40:15,650 --> 00:40:16,490
Why the rush to send a message

890
00:40:16,490 --> 00:40:17,530
to ask me here?

891
00:40:20,370 --> 00:40:21,930
Don't listen to those rumors out there.

892
00:40:21,930 --> 00:40:24,090
There's nothing between Xu Ao and me.

893
00:40:24,350 --> 00:40:25,190
It's just...

894
00:40:25,690 --> 00:40:28,220
I have difficulties
that are hard to explain.

895
00:40:29,020 --> 00:40:30,470
Just wait for me two or three more days,

896
00:40:30,470 --> 00:40:32,130
once I finish what I need to do,

897
00:40:32,330 --> 00:40:33,910
we can run away together.

898
00:40:44,250 --> 00:40:45,830
Ms. Hua, what's troubling you?

899
00:40:45,830 --> 00:40:46,960
Feel free to tell us.

900
00:40:49,920 --> 00:40:52,140
Ms. Hua, won't you be honest with me?

901
00:40:53,110 --> 00:40:55,200
Miss Shi, Chief Lu.

902
00:40:55,590 --> 00:40:57,850
That letter was written
by Feng himself.

903
00:40:58,080 --> 00:40:59,480
What have you done to him?

904
00:40:59,550 --> 00:41:00,810
Rest assured, Ms. Hua.

905
00:41:00,940 --> 00:41:02,270
Mr. Li is safe and sound.

906
00:41:02,510 --> 00:41:03,040
Yuerong.

907
00:41:04,500 --> 00:41:05,270
Feng.

908
00:41:05,500 --> 00:41:06,960
Chief Lu is here to help us.

909
00:41:07,020 --> 00:41:09,350
He can help us
get out of this predicament.

910
00:41:09,590 --> 00:41:10,330
Lu.

911
00:41:11,100 --> 00:41:12,840
These two share a deep bond.

912
00:41:13,090 --> 00:41:14,970
I believe Ms. Hua has her reasons.

913
00:41:17,810 --> 00:41:18,500
Chief Lu.

914
00:41:19,300 --> 00:41:21,700
For everything before, I was indeed wrong.

915
00:41:22,080 --> 00:41:23,570
I deeply apologize.

916
00:41:24,090 --> 00:41:25,350
The reason I did this

917
00:41:25,370 --> 00:41:26,700
is because I was coerced

918
00:41:27,530 --> 00:41:29,090
and have difficulties I cannot speak of.

919
00:41:29,090 --> 00:41:30,140
Who forced you?

920
00:41:30,660 --> 00:41:31,450
Chief Lu.

921
00:41:31,680 --> 00:41:34,340
Please forgive me
for not being able to tell you.

922
00:41:35,440 --> 00:41:36,640
Don't worry, Ms. Hua.

923
00:41:36,760 --> 00:41:37,520
I promise you

924
00:41:37,780 --> 00:41:40,580
I will safely escort
both of you out of the capital.

925
00:41:41,650 --> 00:41:42,850
Not just the two of us,

926
00:41:43,450 --> 00:41:44,780
but our family of three.

927
00:41:47,040 --> 00:41:47,850
Chief Lu.

928
00:41:48,090 --> 00:41:50,110
Just bring Ms. Liu here,

929
00:41:50,210 --> 00:41:51,720
and once the misunderstanding is cleared,

930
00:41:51,720 --> 00:41:53,520
I can complete my task and leave.

931
00:41:54,280 --> 00:41:55,550
Ms. Hua, you're straightforward.

932
00:41:55,550 --> 00:41:56,830
When the truth comes to light,

933
00:41:56,830 --> 00:41:57,830
I will send people

934
00:41:57,840 --> 00:42:00,170
to escort you and Mr. Li
out of the capital.

935
00:42:00,340 --> 00:42:02,940
Then I thank you, Chief Lu and Miss Shi.

936
00:42:05,910 --> 00:42:07,670
We eavesdropped once

937
00:42:07,690 --> 00:42:09,710
and found out that Lord Xu is innocent.

938
00:42:09,710 --> 00:42:12,410
But Ms. Hua refused
to explain the situation,

939
00:42:12,690 --> 00:42:14,860
fortunately Lu discovered the key person

940
00:42:14,860 --> 00:42:15,920
and persuaded her.

941
00:42:16,150 --> 00:42:16,680
Ke,

942
00:42:17,360 --> 00:42:18,230
you were actually the one who noticed

943
00:42:18,230 --> 00:42:20,830
the twin lotus jade pendant
at Ms. Hua's waist.

944
00:42:22,960 --> 00:42:26,700
This pendant is a unique piece from
Xibao Pavilion's Qixi Festival collection.

945
00:42:26,700 --> 00:42:28,500
There are two identical pieces,

946
00:42:28,510 --> 00:42:29,790
meant for lovers.

947
00:42:30,370 --> 00:42:32,780
Ms. Hua and Xu Ao
are not romantically involved,

948
00:42:32,780 --> 00:42:35,070
so there must be someone else she loves.

949
00:42:36,730 --> 00:42:37,730
I'll keep my word.

950
00:42:37,800 --> 00:42:38,320
Ms. Hua,

951
00:42:38,480 --> 00:42:40,220
I will ensure your family's safety.

952
00:42:40,220 --> 00:42:42,100
Chief Lu, Miss Shi,

953
00:42:42,180 --> 00:42:43,980
you've protected my reputation

954
00:42:44,050 --> 00:42:45,530
and arranged a way out for me.

955
00:42:45,530 --> 00:42:46,890
I am deeply grateful.

956
00:42:48,770 --> 00:42:50,550
When all is said and done,
it's all your fault.

957
00:42:50,550 --> 00:42:53,050
Fine, it's all my fault.

958
00:43:08,110 --> 00:43:09,310
Why is it so hot today?

959
00:43:18,880 --> 00:43:20,850
[No.1 Matchmaker in the World]

960
00:43:25,380 --> 00:43:26,040
Mother.

961
00:43:26,260 --> 00:43:28,670
At first, I thought no matter what,

962
00:43:28,690 --> 00:43:30,450
I couldn't let them divorce,

963
00:43:30,690 --> 00:43:32,100
because it would affect your reputation

964
00:43:32,100 --> 00:43:32,390
[No.1 Matchmaker in the World]

965
00:43:32,390 --> 00:43:34,610
and the title
of the No.1 matchmaker in the world.

966
00:43:34,610 --> 00:43:36,850
But when I found out Xu Ao was unfaithful,

967
00:43:36,850 --> 00:43:38,350
I couldn't use Yingying's pain

968
00:43:38,350 --> 00:43:40,410
to protect our family's reputation.

969
00:43:40,690 --> 00:43:43,710
So, if what Yingying said had been true,

970
00:43:44,280 --> 00:43:47,190
I would definitely
have helped the two of them get a divorce.

971
00:43:47,190 --> 00:43:48,030
Ke.

972
00:43:48,440 --> 00:43:51,500
That day when you were
confiding in our ancestors,

973
00:43:51,500 --> 00:43:52,110
[No.1 Matchmaker in the World]

974
00:43:52,110 --> 00:43:54,770
I heard everything
outside the ancestral hall.

975
00:43:55,770 --> 00:43:56,750
So, Mother,

976
00:43:57,150 --> 00:43:59,220
you knew about their divorce matter?

977
00:44:01,170 --> 00:44:02,330
I just hope

978
00:44:02,440 --> 00:44:04,040
that all your decisions

979
00:44:04,360 --> 00:44:05,860
come from your heart,

980
00:44:06,540 --> 00:44:08,140
not because of me

981
00:44:08,480 --> 00:44:09,790
or this title.

982
00:44:09,910 --> 00:44:10,480
[No.1 Matchmaker in the World]

983
00:44:10,480 --> 00:44:12,800
You're the best mother ever.

984
00:44:14,350 --> 00:44:15,410
Then let me ask you,

985
00:44:16,110 --> 00:44:17,540
even if I blame you,

986
00:44:18,280 --> 00:44:20,340
will you still stay true to yourself?

987
00:44:22,050 --> 00:44:22,600
I will.

988
00:44:25,280 --> 00:44:26,610
What a good child.

989
00:44:26,620 --> 00:44:27,360
[No.1 Matchmaker in the World]

990
00:44:27,360 --> 00:44:28,560
You're a matchmaker.

991
00:44:29,280 --> 00:44:30,280
Always remember

992
00:44:30,840 --> 00:44:32,150
that with just a few words,

993
00:44:32,150 --> 00:44:34,960
you can determine someone's happiness
for the rest of their life.

994
00:44:34,960 --> 00:44:37,090
Nothing matters more than sincerity.

995
00:44:37,510 --> 00:44:39,030
Whether it's my reputation

996
00:44:39,030 --> 00:44:41,480
or the glory of being
the No.1 matchmaker in the world,

997
00:44:41,480 --> 00:44:44,360
nothing is more important
than the happiness of two people.

998
00:44:44,360 --> 00:44:46,920
That's the true essence of matchmaking.

999
00:44:57,280 --> 00:44:57,790
Ke.

1000
00:44:59,550 --> 00:45:00,100
Ke.

1001
00:45:01,880 --> 00:45:03,960
You've saved Liu Yingying's marriage,

1002
00:45:03,960 --> 00:45:05,420
why are you still unhappy?

1003
00:45:05,450 --> 00:45:07,340
Lu, why are you here?

1004
00:45:07,670 --> 00:45:09,110
Don't let my brothers find you.

1005
00:45:09,110 --> 00:45:10,880
I originally wanted
to tell you some good news,

1006
00:45:10,880 --> 00:45:12,210
but I heard you sighing.

1007
00:45:12,670 --> 00:45:15,240
Why don't you tell me
what's troubling you?

1008
00:45:16,710 --> 00:45:18,170
How would you understand?

1009
00:45:18,630 --> 00:45:19,960
At weddings,

1010
00:45:19,960 --> 00:45:22,820
I often wish couples
prosperity and many children.

1011
00:45:23,230 --> 00:45:25,070
Yingying's marriage is secure now,

1012
00:45:25,070 --> 00:45:26,870
but they still have no children.

1013
00:45:27,150 --> 00:45:29,230
It shows that in life,
eight or nine times out of ten,

1014
00:45:29,230 --> 00:45:30,550
things don’t go as planned.

1015
00:45:30,550 --> 00:45:33,150
That's exactly the good news
I wanted to tell you.

1016
00:45:33,150 --> 00:45:35,400
I've found a skilled doctor
who has examined Mrs. Xu,

1017
00:45:35,400 --> 00:45:36,670
and there's a treatment available.

1018
00:45:36,670 --> 00:45:38,240
So you don't need to worry too much.

1019
00:45:38,240 --> 00:45:39,640
Xu Ao loves Liu Yingying,

1020
00:45:39,960 --> 00:45:42,540
and doesn't care
that much about having children.

1021
00:45:42,540 --> 00:45:43,140
Really?

1022
00:45:44,630 --> 00:45:46,890
Thank you for resolving their concerns.

1023
00:45:48,920 --> 00:45:50,240
Lu.

1024
00:45:50,630 --> 00:45:51,920
If you were Xu Ao,

1025
00:45:51,970 --> 00:45:53,000
what would you do?

1026
00:45:54,520 --> 00:45:55,580
I would be the same.

1027
00:45:56,400 --> 00:45:58,060
If I could marry the one I love,

1028
00:45:58,400 --> 00:45:59,880
whether we have children or not,

1029
00:45:59,880 --> 00:46:00,990
my devotion would never change.
